{
  "macro_id": "landscaping.materialEstimate",
  "domain": "landscaping",
  "name": "materialEstimate",
  "inputs": {
    "squareFootage": {
      "type": "number"
    },
    "material": {
      "type": "string",
      "maxLength": 40
    }
  },
  "reads_artifact_data": true,
  "invariants": [
    "typeof output === 'object' && output !== null",
    "typeof output.ok === 'boolean'",
    "output.ok === false || typeof output.result.material === 'string'",
    "output.ok === false || typeof output.result.squareFootage === 'number'",
    "output.ok === false || typeof output.result.depthInches === 'number'",
    "output.ok === false || typeof output.result.cubicYards === 'number'",
    "output.ok === false || typeof output.result.bags === 'number'",
    "output.ok === false || typeof output.result.estimatedCost === 'number'",
    "output.ok === false || typeof output.result.deliveryNote === 'string'",
    "output.ok === false || Number.isFinite(output.result.cubicYards)",
    "output.ok === false || Number.isFinite(output.result.bags)",
    "output.ok === false || Number.isFinite(output.result.estimatedCost)"
  ],
  "fuzz_cases": [
    {
      "input": {
        "artifact": {
          "data": {
            "squareFootage": 500,
            "material": "mulch"
          }
        }
      },
      "expect": {
        "ok": true
      }
    },
    {
      "input": {
        "artifact": {
          "data": {
            "squareFootage": 100,
            "material": "topsoil"
          }
        }
      },
      "expect": {
        "ok": true
      }
    },
    {
      "input": {
        "artifact": {
          "data": {}
        }
      },
      "expect": {
        "ok": true
      }
    },
    {
      "input": {
        "artifact": {
          "data": {
            "squareFootage": "Infinity",
            "material": "moon-dust"
          }
        }
      },
      "expect": {
        "ok": false
      }
    }
  ],
  "_note": "Pure compute, reads artifact.data. depthInches from a per-material table (mulch 3 / gravel 2 / topsoil 4 / compost 2 / sand 2; unknown → 3). cubicYards = round((sqft × depth / 12 / 27) × 10)/10; bags = ceil(cubicYards × 13.5); estimatedCost = round(cubicYards × costPerYard) (mulch 35 / gravel 45 / topsoil 30 / compost 40 / sand 35; unknown → 35); deliveryNote = cubicYards>3 ? 'Bulk delivery recommended' : 'Bagged purchase sufficient'. FAIL-CLOSED (fixed 2026-06-28): Number.isFinite guard so a raw Infinity squareFootage can't leak Infinity into cubicYards/bags/estimatedCost (prior `parseFloat()||100` passed Infinity through). MaterialEstimator renders ALL fields above EXACTLY."
}
